<docbook><section><title>StressTestingProducesVirtuosoServerCrash</title><para> </para><bridgehead class="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml:h2">Stability Issues </bridgehead>
<bridgehead class="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml:h3">Stress Testing Produces Virtuoso Server Crash</bridgehead>
<para>If you experience a Virtuoso server crash, contact OpenLink Product Support and provide the following information:</para><para>1.
 Hardware and operating system details for the machine hosting the Virtuoso Universal Server.
2 A copy of the virtuoso.ini file.
3.
 A description of load including sample queries, where possible.
4.
 The output of the status() call made under less than critical load.
</para></section></docbook>